headline: Krispy Kreme (DNUT) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of doughnut chain Krispy Kreme (NASDAQ:DNUT) jumped 2.6% in the afternoon session after the stock's positive momentum continued as Morgan Stanley highlighted the company as a top performer in the restaurant sector, and news emerged of a major sponsorship deal with NASCAR.
